author: SomeOrdinaryGamers
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This was an unexpected video to make since during filming with my friends, Mr Beast decides to visit a good friend of mine just as we leave and gives a tell all interview. I never had high expectations and even with his "responses" I feel very disappointed. Why? Let's find out! Thanks for watching!
Like, Comment and Subscribe for more videos!
title: Mr. Beast's Response Is Terrible...
